    "attributes": {
      "name": "Airbnb Listing",
      "images": [],
      "summary": "The AirbnbListing component defines a detailed data card representing an Airbnb property listing, primarily used to display property information in a consistent format. It showcases key details such as property name, location, type, price per night, ratings, review counts, guest capacity, bedroom and bed counts, bathrooms, photos, amenities, host details, listing date, and description. The listing card features embedded and isolated presentation formats, with the embedded version providing a compact preview and the isolated version offering an expanded view with rich styling and interactive elements. Its primary purpose is to serve as a reusable, customizable display of property listings within listings or marketplaces, enabling users to assess and interact with property details efficiently.",
